OL,3,C'We think it will kill her': Families
OL,4,Cin shock after care home announces
OL,5,Cclosure
OL,7,FFamilies of people living in a care
OL,8,Fhome that is due to close say forcing
OL,9,Ftheir loved-ones to leave and find new
OL,10,Faccommodation will put them under
OL,11,Funbearable strain.
OL,13,FThe management of Acorn Lodge in
OL,14,FFailsworth, Greater Manchester,
OL,15,Fannounced is had sold the building to
OL,16,Fbe renovated and re-purposed.
OL,18,FAll of the current 68 residents, many
OL,19,Fwith dementia, will have to live
OL,20,Felsewhere.
