OL,3,C'We think it will kill her': Families
OL,4,Cin shock after care home announces
OL,5,Cclosure
OL,7,FJakki Hope and Julie Hope's mother
OL,8,FKathleen is one of those residents,
OL,9,Fshe has lived at Acorn Lodge for five
OL,10,Fyears, they are worried the move will
OL,11,Fkill the 85-year-old.
OL,13,F"We think it'll kill her if she has to
OL,14,Fmove, we think she'll die," Julie
OL,15,Fsaid. "That's what we're worried
OL,16,Fabout, she's 85."
OL,18,FJakki added: "It's absolutely
OL,19,Fterrible, we couldn't believe (the
OL,20,Fhome is closing), we thought it was a
OL,21,Fjoke, a rumour, but no, it's true."
