OL,3,C'We think it will kill her': Families
OL,4,Cin shock after care home announces
OL,5,Cclosure
OL,7,FSharon Freakes' 88 year-old father,
OL,8,Fwho also has dementia, has lived at
OL,9,FAcorn Lodge for nine months.
OL,11,FShe said: "Everyone is just hurting
OL,12,Finside, thinking how are we going to
OL,13,Ftell them? It's just unthinkable."
OL,15,FHer father currently needs a special
OL,16,FElderly Mentally Infirm (EMI) bed at
OL,17,Fthe unit because he has a particular
OL,18,Fadvanced stage of dementia.
OL,20,FShe worries that they will struggle to
OL,21,Ffind him these resources elsewhere.
