OL,3,C'We think it will kill her': Families
OL,4,Cin shock after care home announces
OL,5,Cclosure
OL,7,FLinda Walsh and Barbara Hatch are
OL,8,Fsisters whose mother lives at Acorn
OL,9,FLodge.
OL,11,FThey say the home provides a great
OL,12,Fstandard of care, the staff work well
OL,13,Fand the residents are happy where they
OL,14,Fare.
OL,16,FThey believe having to move could
OL,17,F"kill" their mother.
OL,19,F"It's a brilliant home, it's very
OL,20,Ffamily oriented, each unit has their
OL,21,Fown little family," Linda said.
