OL,5,Cclosure
OL,7,F"It will kill a lot of them
OL,8,F(residents) in there, because they are
OL,9,Freally, really upset."
OL,11,FThe home's management cite financial
OL,12,Ffor the closure, and said funding for
OL,13,Fthe sector had not "kept pace" with
OL,14,Finflation and the cost of living.
