OL,3,C'We think it will kill her': Families
OL,4,Cin shock after care home announces
OL,5,Cclosure
OL,7,FIn a statement it said: "We have made
OL,8,FOldham Council aware that we, as
OL,9,Fowners of the Acorn Lodge Nursing
OL,10,FHome, have agreed a sale of Acorn
OL,11,FLodge to Exemplar Health Care who plan
OL,12,Fto extensively refurbish and renovate
OL,13,Fthe home and re-open it as a
OL,14,Fspecialist home for adults living with
OL,15,Facquired brain injuries, neurological
OL,16,Fconditions, dementia and physical
OL,17,Fdisabilities.
