OL,3,C'We think it will kill her': Families
OL,4,Cin shock after care home announces
OL,5,Cclosure
OL,7,F"It was for this reason that we had
OL,8,Fmade the difficult decision to sell
OL,9,Fthe home, before any financial
OL,10,Fstruggles started and whilst we could
OL,11,Fstill ensure the highest quality of
OL,12,Fservice and care."
OL,14,FOldham Council said that while they
OL,15,Fare frustrated at the short notice of
OL,16,Fthe announcement to close Acorn Lodge,
OL,17,Fthey cannot prevent it being closed.
OL,19,FIt added it was now working to try and
OL,20,Fre-home residents as quickly as
OL,21,Fpossible.
